ActAn Act to amend the Criminal Code, the DNA Identification Act and the National Defence Act
An Act to amend certain Acts in relation to DNA identification
PrecisOrder fixes January 1, 2008 as the day on which certain provisions of An Act to amend the Criminal Code, the DNA IDENTIFICATION ACT and NATIONAL DEFENCE ACT and of AN ACT to amend certain Acts in relation to DNA identification come in force.
